    "Not all study differences are observable.",
    "Although the analysis results reported in Table 2 show considerable heterogeneity across subgroups, most variables do not appear to moderate the effects reported in Table 3.",
    "Information on variables such as gender, ethnicity, disadvantaged status, grades, dosage, and school religious identity were available only from a limited number of studies.",
